headline: Saudi Arabia Vision Care Market Forecast and Company Analysis Report 2025-2033 Featuring Essilor, J&J, Bausch Health, Novartis, Grand Vision, Carl Zeiss, Valeant, Paragon Vision Science, Menicon
summary: The Saudi Arabia Vision Care Market is projected to grow from US$ 899.58 million in 2024 to US$ 1.29 billion by 2033, driven by a CAGR of 4.11% from 2025 to 2033. Key growth factors include an aging population, rising eye disorders due to increased screen time, technological advancements, and supportive government initiatives under Vision 2030. The market is segmented by product types such as Glass Lenses and Lasik Equipment, and distribution channels like Retail Stores and E-Commerce. Challenge
